I"ö<p>This project titled <strong>The Conurbation Algorithm</strong> is aimed at developing a fully functional featured city without disrupting the ecological density of the city. It was the winning project of my first hackathon <strong>Electrothon 2k20</strong> at NIT Hamirpur. It is a further modification of the initial <a href="https://github.com/josauder/procedural_city_generation">city generation model</a>.</p>

<p>In this blog I shall give a brief overview of the workflow of this project. I am <strong>not</strong> going <strong>to touch the coding part</strong> as of now so as to prevent the things from being more complicated to comprehend.</p>

