<h2 id="-1"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.5%7C3.6%7C3.7-success" alt="Python Badge" /><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Dependencies-NumPy%20%7C%20PyQt5%20%7C%20Blender%20%7C%20Scipy%20%7C%20Matplotlib-ff69b4" alt="Dependency" /></h2>

